Mislintat on why he left Arsenal: &quot;Last summer there were leadership changes at #Arsenal. It had been agreed I would become technical director, so I would be around the team on a daily basis. But the new leadership had their own agenda &amp; other candidates&quot;<br />
<br />
Mislintat: &quot;On top of that, we had different approaches. Previously we had a strong systematic approach to transfers, a mixture of watching things live as well as quality data &amp; video analysis &ndash; #Arsenal actually owns their own data company&quot;

